### Cadastrar funcionário 1
POST http://localhost:8080/funcionarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Carlos Almeida",
  "email": "carlos@pizzly.com",
  "telefone": "(74) 99999-1111",
  "senha": "12345678",
  "matricula": "FUNC001",
  "perfil": "ADMINISTRADOR"
}

